  "title": "fix: remove a warning about insights that is not relevant anymore",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for submitting a pull request!\r\n  Please provide enough information so that others can review your pull request.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR removes a warning about insights that is not relevant anymore.\r\nThe warning message was useful when user added `search-insights` but forgot to pass to `insightsClient` prop to `instantsearch()` call, but now that we don't encourage that prop anymore in favor of insights middleware, this warning message misleads those who use insights middleware.",
